{"tid":232582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（來生不做非洲人）坦桑尼亞車禍，32小學童雞死","createTime":"2017-05-06T22:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T06:36:14.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"241cff0da8d2bf55675c59f19b7127dc1ef022e4","tid":232582,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T22:34:24.000Z","msg":"一架滿載學童的巴士，在非洲坦桑尼亞北部失控衝出路面撞毀，至少造成35人死亡，大部份是小學生。<br />\n<br />\n當地官員說，巴士當時載著一間小學的學生往參加考試，在一條河邊滑出路面肇禍，死者包括32名學生、兩名教師和巴士司機。"},{"pid":"c34f168641518dd378a9685c5549695e55828e3c","tid":232582,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T22:40:21.000Z","msg":"話知佢可以復活有2條非洲命<br />\n都唔揀非洲人啦<br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9392013212c654f70efcd2de15ef7758b60b6560","tid":232582,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9764e25b296319ce14fffa0bdca5372812e216","tid":232582,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:23:50.000Z","msg":"早日投胎是福<br />\n來生別做有色人"},{"pid":"e12faf4f8a73baa223f35c0ac8b5318cf5a5b3e4","tid":232582,"uid":56107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早日投胎是福<br />\n來生別做有色人</blockquote><br />\n做透明人咪仲慘<br />\n成世畀人無視<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ada92ac9fb0653dee5df8e5fb83bb475f8b6830","tid":232582,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3395c37489bccce3ff28bef150d67f0886106c37","tid":232582,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"港女唔捐埋副身家俾佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c5ba1dc8a133795e0b44b22c89f29f4d375